# Privacy Policy

**Last Updated:** [أدخل التاريخ]

This Privacy Policy describes how [Super DEV] ("the Bot") collects, uses, and shares information when you use our service.

## 1. Information We Collect

### Automatically Collected Information:
- **Server ID**: To identify which Discord server is using the Bot
- **User ID**: To process commands and manage permissions
- **Command Usage**: Basic data about which commands are used and when
- **Voice Channel ID**: To connect and stream audio in voice channels

### We DO NOT Collect:
- Message content
- Personal information beyond what Discord provides
- Payment information
- Location data

## 2. How We Use Information

The collected information is used solely for:
- Operating and maintaining the Bot's functionality
- Providing radio streaming services in voice channels
- Improving Bot performance and user experience
- Preventing abuse and ensuring compliance with Discord's Terms
- Debugging and technical support

## 3. Data Storage and Security

- All data is stored securely using Discord's API
- We implement industry-standard security measures
- Data is retained only as long as necessary for Bot operation
- We do not sell, trade, or rent user data to third parties

## 4. Third-Party Services

The Bot uses:
- **Discord API**: Subject to Discord's Privacy Policy
- **Hosting Services**: [Railway]
- **Radio Streams**: Publicly available radio links (subject to their respective policies)

## 5. Cookies and Tracking

The Bot does not use cookies or tracking technologies beyond Discord's standard API functionality.

## 6. Your Rights

You have the right to:
- Remove the Bot from your server at any time
- Request deletion of your data by contacting us
- Opt-out of non-essential data collection

## 7. Data Retention

- Command logs: Retained for [30 days / 90 days] for debugging purposes
- Server/User IDs: Retained while the Bot is active in your server
- Usage statistics: Anonymized and retained for service improvement

## 8. Children's Privacy

The Bot is not intended for users under 13 years old. We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, contact us immediately.

## 9. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of significant changes by:
- Updating the "Last Updated" date
- Posting an announcement in our support server (if applicable)
- Continued use of the Bot constitutes acceptance of the updated policy

## 10. Contact Us

If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to request data deletion, contact us at:

- **Support Server:** [https://discord.gg/udcDqmenG]


## 11. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)

For users in the European Economic Area (EEA), our legal basis for collecting and using information is:
- Performance of a contract (providing Bot services)
- Legitimate interests (improving service, preventing abuse)
- Consent (where applicable)

## 12. International Data Transfers

Data may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your own. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your information in accordance with this policy.

